4:7 kai\ h( ei)rh/nh tou= qeou= h( u(pere/xousa pa/nta nou=n frourh/sei ta\j kardi/aj u(mw=n kai\ ta\ noh/mata u(mw=n e)n Xristw=| )Ihsou=. 4:8 To\ loipo/n, a)delfoi/, o(/sa e)sti\n a)lhqh=, o(/sa semna/, o(/sa di/kaia, o(/sa a(gna/, o(/sa prosfilh=, o(/sa eu)/fhma, ei)/ tij a)reth\ kai\ ei)/ tij e)/painoj, tau=ta logi/zesqe:
