4:10 )Exa/rhn de\ e)n kuri/w| mega/lwj o(/ti h)/dh pote\ a)neqa/lete to\ u(pe\r e)mou= fronei=n, e)f' w(=| kai\ e)fronei=te h)kairei=sqe de/.
